articles.title: Two Americans held in Afghanistan traded for Taliban prisoner in final Biden deal delayed until Trump took office - CNN
articles.description: In the very last hours of President Joe Biden’s time in office, a prisoner exchange years in the making was finally struck: the Taliban agreed to swap two Americans being held in Afghanistan for one Taliban member serving a life sentence in a US prison.
